WEBVTT

00:02.369 --> 00:03.368
[ Remote clicks ]

00:03.403 --> 00:04.937
[ Upbeat music plays ]

00:07.507 --> 00:10.376
♪ I don't care what you say! ♪

00:11.711 --> 00:13.678
♪ I'm gonna do what I want
all day! ♪

00:13.713 --> 00:16.314
♪ I'm the king of the world!
I'm the king of the world! ♪

00:16.349 --> 00:18.216
♪ I'm the king of the world!
I'm the king of the world! ♪

00:18.251 --> 00:22.688
♪ I'm the king of the world!
I'm the king of the world! ♪

00:24.590 --> 00:27.225
[ Surf music plays ]

00:28.929 --> 00:30.695
[ Indistinct conversations ]

00:30.730 --> 00:31.696
Aah!

00:31.731 --> 00:32.998
Why won't it rinse out?!

00:33.033 --> 00:34.566
[ Air blowing ]

00:34.601 --> 00:36.401
Aaaaaaah!

00:36.436 --> 00:39.538
Clarence: - [ Chuckles ] I can't
wait to get into the hot tub.

00:39.573 --> 00:42.374
I'm gonna make something
that I call "Clarence Soup."

00:42.409 --> 00:43.875
I'll let you have
a little bit,

00:43.910 --> 00:45.343
[ Singsong voice ]
but guess what.

00:45.378 --> 00:47.245
You can't know what
the secret ingredient is.

00:47.280 --> 00:48.713
Nice and tight, Sumo.

00:48.748 --> 00:51.383
I don't want any chlorine
burning my eyes. [ Chuckles ]

00:51.418 --> 00:54.386
This time, I'm gonna do a flip
off the diving board!

00:54.421 --> 00:56.088
But wait --
aren't you afraid

00:56.123 --> 00:57.556
everyone's gonna
see your butt again?

00:57.591 --> 00:59.624
Nope. Not this time.

00:59.659 --> 01:01.693
[ Breathing heavily ]

01:01.728 --> 01:02.727
Hey, y'all.

01:02.762 --> 01:03.895
Oh. Hi, Samuel.

01:03.930 --> 01:05.030
Hey, hey, guys.

01:05.065 --> 01:06.465
Guess what
my dad told me.

01:06.500 --> 01:08.467
I learned, if you bring
a plastic zip bag,

01:08.502 --> 01:10.769
you can put
- whatever you want in there.

01:10.804 --> 01:12.571
[ Muffled ] - And if it's in the
pool, it won't get wrecked.

01:12.606 --> 01:14.206
♪ Oh, Samuel ♪
That's pretty tight!

01:14.241 --> 01:15.907
[ Laughter ]

01:15.942 --> 01:17.409
What?

01:17.444 --> 01:18.443
[ Laughs ]

01:18.478 --> 01:19.377
Whew!

01:19.412 --> 01:20.278
Well,
see y'all out there.

01:20.313 --> 01:21.646
Both: See ya! Bye!

01:21.681 --> 01:22.647
Ohh.

01:22.682 --> 01:24.616
Samuel is so funny.

01:24.651 --> 01:25.817
He sure is.

01:25.852 --> 01:28.386
One time, I saw him do
this huge cannonball.

01:28.421 --> 01:30.789
There was like two drops
of water left in the pool!

01:30.824 --> 01:33.091
Mm-hmm.

01:33.126 --> 01:36.495
[ Laughter,
indistinct shouting ]

01:41.968 --> 01:43.969
Marco!
- Polo.

01:44.004 --> 01:45.270
Fish out of water?

01:45.305 --> 01:47.472
No, I'm totally
in the water still.

01:47.507 --> 01:48.773
Aw, come on!

01:48.808 --> 01:50.442
[ Chuckles ]

01:50.477 --> 01:52.611
Soup, soup, soup,
soup, soup, soup!

01:52.646 --> 01:54.613
Got to make the soup. Got to make the soup!
All you people. Ugh.

01:54.648 --> 01:57.115
Whoa, kid!
Check out the sign, bud!

01:57.150 --> 01:59.251
No kids
without supervision!

01:59.286 --> 02:00.819
What?
What sign?

02:00.854 --> 02:02.087
Oh.

02:02.122 --> 02:03.688
But --
But<i> he's</i> a grown-up.

02:03.723 --> 02:06.925
Sir, are you prepared to take
responsibility for this child?

02:06.960 --> 02:09.127
Leave me alone!

02:09.162 --> 02:10.762
Aw, Christmas.

02:10.797 --> 02:12.497
Hey. I get it.

02:12.532 --> 02:14.599
You just want
to play around for a bit.

02:14.634 --> 02:16.601
Nothing bad's
gonna happen, right?

02:16.636 --> 02:17.836
I hear ya, Kemosabe.

02:17.871 --> 02:19.137
[ Gasps ] You do?

02:19.172 --> 02:20.539
I hear you
with both my ears, man.

02:20.574 --> 02:22.507
But it's a slippery slope,
my main brother.

02:22.542 --> 02:25.644
First [Chuckles] I let you
in the hot tub without an adult.

02:25.679 --> 02:26.678
Then, before I know it,

02:26.713 --> 02:28.647
I'm digging kids' bodies
out of the deep end.

02:28.682 --> 02:29.814
[ Eerie music plays ]

02:29.849 --> 02:32.784
It's all about
- combining fun with safety.

02:32.819 --> 02:33.885
You feel me?

02:33.920 --> 02:35.987
[ Sighs ] Okay.

02:36.022 --> 02:38.190
This place may
be swimming with guards,

02:38.225 --> 02:41.860
but Clarence Soup
is still on the menu.

02:41.895 --> 02:44.062
Jeff, are you coming?

02:44.097 --> 02:45.363
I-I'll get there.

02:45.398 --> 02:47.332
Just gonna go
at my own pace.

02:47.367 --> 02:48.400
The water's
a bit chilly.

02:48.435 --> 02:49.634
[ Breathing heavily ]

02:49.669 --> 02:50.802
Hey, guys!

02:50.837 --> 02:52.003
[ Grunts ]

02:52.038 --> 02:54.806
Cannonball!
[ Surf music plays ]

02:54.841 --> 02:57.576
[ Laughs maniacally ]

02:57.611 --> 03:00.011
[ Screaming ]

03:00.046 --> 03:01.913
Ohh!

03:01.948 --> 03:03.815
Pshew! Pshew! Pshew!

03:03.850 --> 03:05.384
Whoosh! Whoosh! Whoosh!

03:08.188 --> 03:09.888
All right!
Come at me, Sumo!

03:09.923 --> 03:10.922
Yaaaaah!

03:10.957 --> 03:12.924
[ Laughs ]

03:12.959 --> 03:14.025
Hey, man.

03:14.060 --> 03:15.427
What's with
the belly bag?

03:15.462 --> 03:17.896
What, this?
Oh, it's nothing.

03:17.931 --> 03:19.598
It's ju--
[ Screams ]

03:19.633 --> 03:22.000
I got you, man. I got your pits.
[ Gasping ]

03:22.035 --> 03:23.835
Oh. What happened?

03:23.870 --> 03:26.571
Kid got too close
to the deep end.

03:26.606 --> 03:27.772
Deep end?

03:27.807 --> 03:29.207
How deep is it?

03:29.242 --> 03:32.010
Nobody knows.
Some say it never ends.

03:32.045 --> 03:34.346
Pretty sure there's still kids
at the bottom,

03:34.381 --> 03:35.747
but you can't
see 'em.

03:35.782 --> 03:37.616
Wow.

03:37.651 --> 03:38.717
[ Thud ]

03:39.819 --> 03:41.486
[ Laughs ]

03:42.589 --> 03:44.623
[ Chuckles ]

03:46.092 --> 03:47.759
[ Laughs ]

03:47.794 --> 03:49.561
<i>Ew! I can see his butt!</i>

03:49.596 --> 03:51.029
<i>[ Gasps ] Oh, my goodness.</i>

03:51.064 --> 03:52.397
<i>Somebody get him a towel!</i>

03:52.432 --> 03:54.199
<i>Hurry, hurry! Quick!</i>

03:54.234 --> 03:57.068
Uh, I forgot --
I got to pee.

03:57.103 --> 03:58.770
What a wienie.

03:58.805 --> 04:00.905
[ Sizzling ]

04:00.940 --> 04:03.241
Mm-mmm!

04:03.276 --> 04:04.442
Actually, um,

04:04.477 --> 04:05.944
could I get
some mustard packets?

04:05.979 --> 04:08.413
Oh, and if you have
any extra jalapeños, too,

04:08.448 --> 04:09.748
I'd appreciate that.

04:09.783 --> 04:12.050
Oh, actually,
I changed my mind.

04:12.085 --> 04:13.785
I don't want these
anymore.

04:13.820 --> 04:15.086
Actually...

04:15.121 --> 04:18.156
Hey, Sumo, did you go off
the diving board yet?

04:18.191 --> 04:20.225
No way!
Never going on that thing!

04:20.260 --> 04:21.493
What?

04:21.528 --> 04:22.927
You can't just give up
on your dream --

04:22.962 --> 04:25.130
just like I won't give up
on<i> my</i> dream.

04:25.165 --> 04:26.231
But --

04:26.266 --> 04:27.999
Sumo, remember...

04:28.034 --> 04:29.267
[ Grunts ]

04:29.302 --> 04:31.269
...you are what you do.

04:31.304 --> 04:33.905
A kid is defined
by his actions,

04:33.940 --> 04:35.273
not his memory.

04:35.308 --> 04:37.843
Take my hand, please.

04:39.145 --> 04:41.780
[ Grunts ] Open your mind.
[ Eerie music plays ]

04:41.815 --> 04:43.281
What are you doing, man?

04:43.316 --> 04:44.416
I saw it on TV.

04:44.451 --> 04:46.651
Open your mind.

04:46.686 --> 04:47.786
Eh...

04:47.821 --> 04:50.855
Open your mind.

04:50.890 --> 04:57.696
Open...your...mind.

04:57.731 --> 05:00.298
Open your...

05:00.333 --> 05:02.133
Hey, uh,
- could I get a fry?

05:02.168 --> 05:03.501
Ha ha! Sure, man! - Ow!

05:03.536 --> 05:05.303
Have all you want!
- Quit it, Sumo!

05:05.338 --> 05:07.205
Oye, mijo.

05:07.240 --> 05:09.974
Could you please
help me, por favor?

05:10.009 --> 05:13.778
"Clarence, help!
I'm a hungry back man!"

05:13.813 --> 05:15.146
Here you go.

05:15.181 --> 05:16.147
[ Babbles ]

05:16.182 --> 05:18.450
Ay! This is feeling...

05:18.485 --> 05:20.352
[ Snoring ]
[ Groans ]

05:21.988 --> 05:24.989
Sumo!
Don't forget.

05:25.024 --> 05:26.858
[ Eerie music plays ]

05:30.196 --> 05:31.896
Huh?

05:31.931 --> 05:32.964
[ Excited chatter ]

05:32.999 --> 05:35.066
[ Sighs ]

05:35.101 --> 05:36.901
Backward flip!

05:36.936 --> 05:38.069
[ Gasps ]
Whoa!

05:38.104 --> 05:40.638
[ Cheering ]

05:40.673 --> 05:42.173
Not bad.

05:42.208 --> 05:43.875
Oh. [ Chuckles ]

05:43.910 --> 05:45.744
Sumo! Come on! Yeah!

05:45.779 --> 05:48.246
[ Laughs ]

05:48.281 --> 05:50.315
[ Inhaling ]

05:50.350 --> 05:51.316
[ Both laugh ]

05:51.351 --> 05:52.550
Hey, killer flip, man.

05:52.585 --> 05:54.419
You got it, man.
You get it.

05:54.454 --> 05:55.687
Hey, thanks, man.

05:55.722 --> 05:58.356
Now you got to go off
the<i> big</i> one.

05:58.391 --> 05:59.924
Aaaahh!
[ Splash ]

05:59.959 --> 06:02.193
Uh...yeah, maybe.

06:02.228 --> 06:03.528
Oh, my gosh.

06:03.563 --> 06:05.864
That's the best idea
I ever heard, Samuel!

06:05.899 --> 06:08.032
Oh, Sumo, it's gonna be so cool.
Mnh-mnh, mnh-mnh.

06:08.067 --> 06:10.402
You're gonna go up
to the biggest one ever,

06:10.437 --> 06:12.270
and you're gonna be up
really, really high

06:12.305 --> 06:14.372
and then see
all the birds in the sky.

06:14.407 --> 06:17.208
And everyone's gonna be like,
"Oh, my gosh, look at Sumo!

06:17.243 --> 06:18.376
He's so high up there!

06:18.411 --> 06:20.044
I can't believe
how high he got up!"

06:20.079 --> 06:23.348
[ Babbling ]

06:23.383 --> 06:25.683
[ Laughs maniacally ]

06:25.718 --> 06:28.119
[ Breathing heavily ]

06:28.154 --> 06:29.354
You're gonna do it,
right?

06:29.389 --> 06:31.289
Uh...

06:31.324 --> 06:32.724
yep.

06:32.759 --> 06:34.192
All right!
- [ Laughs ] Yes!

06:34.227 --> 06:36.294
Looking forward to seeing you
perched up there, buddy.

06:36.329 --> 06:38.730
Bye, Samuel!
You're so cool!

06:39.499 --> 06:41.099
Ow!
- What the heck, man?!

06:41.134 --> 06:42.400
What was that for?

06:42.435 --> 06:44.135
You want<i> me</i>
to go off of<i> that?!</i>

06:44.170 --> 06:45.937
[ Screams ]

06:45.972 --> 06:47.038
[ Splash ]

06:47.073 --> 06:49.641
But, Sumo,
- you're a flip-diving king,

06:49.676 --> 06:51.543
and you're
the best one ever.

06:51.578 --> 06:53.244
It's gonna be awesome,
and --

06:53.279 --> 06:58.917
and it's gonna be impressive
and cool and bubbly and...

06:58.952 --> 07:03.788
It's got the jets,
and it's...hot soup...

07:03.823 --> 07:04.923
Clarence Soup.

07:04.958 --> 07:06.090
What?

07:06.125 --> 07:07.659
Anyway, good luck!

07:07.694 --> 07:10.895
Hey! Clarence,
those are mine!

07:10.930 --> 07:14.098
[ Breathes deeply,
exhales sharply ]

07:14.133 --> 07:16.001
[ Eerie music plays ]

07:18.438 --> 07:20.772
[ Grunts ]
Feel the burn.

07:20.807 --> 07:21.906
[ Grunts ]

07:21.941 --> 07:23.642
Oh, oh!

07:33.353 --> 07:35.620
[ Thinking ]<i> Okay, okay,</i>
<i>what was Clarence saying?</i>

07:35.655 --> 07:38.289
<i>Clear your -- Clear your head?</i>

07:38.324 --> 07:39.757
<i>O-Open the thoughts?</i>

07:39.792 --> 07:42.927
Hey! Stop splashing!
I'm going in at my own pace.

07:42.962 --> 07:44.195
Aah!

07:44.230 --> 07:46.030
[ Up-tempo music plays ]

07:46.065 --> 07:47.031
Aah! Aah!

07:47.066 --> 07:49.033
Oh -- Aah!

07:49.068 --> 07:50.802
[ Gasping ]

07:50.837 --> 07:51.669
Oh!

07:51.704 --> 07:52.837
[ Screaming ]
Mmm.

07:52.872 --> 07:55.340
[ Gasps ]
Another dangler?!

07:55.375 --> 07:58.142
Whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa!

07:58.177 --> 08:00.144
Well done, Sumo.

08:00.179 --> 08:02.146
The perfect distraction.

08:02.181 --> 08:04.983
It's time to journey
to the hot tub.

08:05.018 --> 08:07.018
[ Thinking ]
<i>Okay, here I go.</i>

08:07.053 --> 08:08.152
<i>I'm just gonna...</i>

08:08.187 --> 08:09.854
<i>Wait a minute.</i>
[ Eerie music plays ]

08:09.889 --> 08:12.524
<i>What's this strange pull</i>
<i>I feel?</i>

08:12.559 --> 08:16.160
<i>It...feels good...</i>

08:16.195 --> 08:18.997
<i>calming, quiet.</i>

08:19.032 --> 08:22.567
<i>I could just...disappear</i>
<i>down here.</i>

08:22.602 --> 08:24.369
<i>It feels like home.</i>

08:24.404 --> 08:26.004
<i>And all my friends are here.</i>

08:26.039 --> 08:28.840
<i>Hi, Clarence!</i>
<i>Hi, Clarence!  Hi, Clarence!</i>

08:28.875 --> 08:30.875
Whoa! Aah!

08:30.910 --> 08:31.976
[ Babbles ]

08:32.011 --> 08:33.378
Come on, come on!

08:33.413 --> 08:34.679
Hey, kiddo.

08:34.714 --> 08:37.148
This is a no-dangle zone,
capiche?

08:37.183 --> 08:38.583
Come on down -- now!

08:38.618 --> 08:41.152
[ Grunts ]

08:41.187 --> 08:43.688
<i>Open your mind.</i>
[ Eerie music plays ]

08:43.723 --> 08:46.491
<i>Open your mind.</i>

08:46.526 --> 08:47.525
Okay.

08:47.560 --> 08:48.526
[ Grunts ]

08:48.561 --> 08:50.061
Gotcha! Huh?

08:51.864 --> 08:53.264
Ha ha!

08:53.299 --> 08:54.832
Cannonball!

08:54.867 --> 08:57.035
[ Laughs ]
You did it, man!

08:57.070 --> 08:58.036
[ Laughing ] Hey!

08:58.071 --> 08:59.871
That's my Sumster
right there.

08:59.906 --> 09:02.106
[ Thinking ]<i> Thank you so much</i>
<i>for having me down here.</i>

09:02.141 --> 09:04.709
<i>I guess I could...</i>
<i>get used to it.</i>

09:04.744 --> 09:07.045
<i>Happy birthday, Ms. Quarter.</i>

09:07.080 --> 09:10.415
[ Angelic choir vocalizing ]
<i>Wait! What...</i>

09:10.450 --> 09:12.283
<i>Uh...w-wait!</i>

09:12.318 --> 09:15.219
<i>I can't stay here!</i>
<i>I'm almost at the hot tub!</i>

09:15.254 --> 09:17.221
[ Cheering ]

09:17.256 --> 09:18.623
Ha ha! Yeah!

09:18.658 --> 09:20.058
Okay. All right, man.

09:20.093 --> 09:21.626
Time to cover up, buddy.
Come here.

09:21.661 --> 09:23.394
Hey! Hey, wait!
Get back here!

09:23.429 --> 09:24.395
[ Laughter, cheering ]

09:24.430 --> 09:27.065
[ Gasps ] Whew!

09:27.100 --> 09:28.199
Come on, man!

09:28.234 --> 09:30.401
The moon doesn't rise
for five hours!

09:30.436 --> 09:32.203
Pbhhhhhht!

09:32.238 --> 09:33.438
[ Gasps ]

09:33.473 --> 09:35.273
I'm finally here.

09:35.308 --> 09:37.575
[ Chuckles ]

09:37.610 --> 09:39.577
[ Singsong voice ]
Clarence Soup time!

09:39.612 --> 09:41.079
<i>♪ Vegetables ♪</i>

09:41.114 --> 09:42.947
[ Grunts ]

09:42.982 --> 09:44.415
Ha! Yeah!

09:44.450 --> 09:45.783
Soup, soup, soup, soup, soup!

09:45.818 --> 09:47.118
Soup's on!
- Hey!

09:47.153 --> 09:48.486
[ Laughs ]
- Hey!

09:48.521 --> 09:49.621
It's Clarence Soup!

09:49.656 --> 09:50.822
Almost.

09:50.857 --> 09:52.390
Just one last step.

09:52.425 --> 09:53.424
[ Laughs ]

09:53.459 --> 09:54.959
Sumo!

09:54.994 --> 09:55.893
[ Sighs ]

09:55.928 --> 09:57.428
It's not actually that cold.

09:57.463 --> 09:58.429
[ Chuckles ]

09:58.464 --> 10:00.264
Hey.
- Oh!

10:00.299 --> 10:02.400
[ Laughs ]
- Oh, you sure got me, Jeffrey.

10:02.435 --> 10:03.468
[ Laughs ]

10:03.503 --> 10:05.269
[ Sighs deeply ]

10:05.304 --> 10:06.270
[ Gulps ]

10:06.305 --> 10:07.271
Hey, man. 'Sup?

10:07.306 --> 10:08.773
Hoo! First customer.

10:08.808 --> 10:12.143
Would you like to sample
my famous Clarence Soup, sir?

10:12.178 --> 10:13.945
[ Slurps ]

10:13.980 --> 10:16.114
[ Spits ]

10:16.149 --> 10:17.749
It's pretty good.

10:17.784 --> 10:21.686
[ Whispering ]
- The secret ingredient is me.

10:21.721 --> 10:23.588
[ Laughs ] Hey, man!

10:23.623 --> 10:25.423
That was hi-larious!

10:25.458 --> 10:26.758
It was awesome,
my Sumster.

10:26.793 --> 10:29.527
You were all, "Whoo!"

10:29.562 --> 10:30.628
[ Laughs ]

10:30.663 --> 10:31.796
Thanks, Samuel.

10:31.831 --> 10:33.464
Hey, come on, man.
Bring it in.

10:33.499 --> 10:34.766
You little knucklehead!

10:34.801 --> 10:36.267
Yeah, got you right here.
[ Laughs ]

10:36.302 --> 10:37.368
Hey, man, cut it out!

10:37.403 --> 10:38.636
Hey, you guys!

10:38.671 --> 10:39.804
Huh?
- Huh?            Huh?

10:39.839 --> 10:41.639
Come on!
What are you waiting for?

10:41.674 --> 10:43.274
Get in the pool already!

10:43.309 --> 10:46.511
[ Laughter ]

10:46.546 --> 10:49.247
[ Excited chatter ]

10:52.552 --> 10:54.686
[ Crickets chirping ]

10:59.726 --> 11:01.559
Man, I hate summer.

11:01.594 --> 11:03.161
[ Splash ]

11:04.363 --> 11:06.364
♪ Early to bed ♪

11:07.600 --> 11:10.101
♪ Early to rise ♪

11:11.571 --> 11:14.773
♪ Picking my nose ♪
